JOHANNESBURG, South Africa, March 4, 2022/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            30,153 tests were conducted in the last 24hrs, with 1,898 new cases, which represents a 6.3% positivity rate. Today @HealthZA reports 18 deaths; of which 2 occurred in the past 24–48 hrs. Total fatalities are 99,517 to date: https://nicd.ac.za/latest-confirmed-cases-of-covid-19-in-south-africa-4-march-2022/